tandard were higher than today just a mere 30 years ago or so, check what the mortgage rates were in the 70's and 80's.  Wages and home prices due to lack of stock are the primary issues here.</p><p>Also why are you blaming the admin for interest rates? That's up to the fed right? Are you advocating for the President to be able to set interest rates unilaterally? Are you a monarchist?</p></div>
